                  <handDesc hands="2">
                     <summary>Tvær hendur.</summary>
                     <handNote scope="sole" script="textualis" scribe="unknown">I. <locus from="1r" facs="#AM04-0720a-VIII-0001r" to="1v">1r-v</locus>: Óþekktur skrifari, textaskrift.</handNote>
                     <handNote scope="sole" script="textualis" scribe="unknown">II. <locus from="2r" facs="#AM04-0720a-VIII-0002r" to="2v">2r-v</locus>: Óþekktur skrifari, textaskrift.</handNote>
